<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>ELID Â· Cronograma ENAMED 2026</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;1,400&family=Raleway:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Great+Vibes&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --plum:#2d1b2e; --plum-2:#3a2640; --plum-soft:#42304a;
    --rose:#b76e79; --rose-bright:#cf8593; --mauve:#c9a0b0; --ivory:#faf6f0;
    --ok:#5fb98f; --ok-bg:rgba(95,185,143,.16);
    --warn:#d8a657; --urgent:#d77a7a; --lilac:#a78bc4;
    --line:rgba(201,160,176,.18); --card:rgba(201,160,176,.06);
    --font-d:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; --font-b:'Raleway',sans-serif; --font-s:'Great Vibes',cursive;
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
  html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
  body{font-family:var(--font-b);color:var(--ivory);
    background:radial-gradient(1200px 600px at 80% -10%,rgba(183,110,121,.18),transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(900px 500px at -10% 100%,rgba(201,160,176,.12),transparent 55%),var(--plum);
    min-height:100vh;line-height:1.55;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;padding-bottom:60px}
  .wrap{max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 20px}
  header{padding:34px 0 14px;text-align:center}
  .rod{display:block;margin:0 auto 12px;color:var(--rose)}
  .brand{font-family:var(--font-d);font-size:46px;font-weight:300;letter-spacing:.18em;line-height:1}
  .brand .hl{color:var(--rose-bright)}
  .tag{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.3em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mauve);margin-top:8px}
  .ded{font-family:var(--font-s);font-size:21px;color:var(--mauve);margin-top:8px}
  .ded .hl{color:var(--rose-bright);font-style:normal}
  .countdown{margin:20px auto 4px;display:flex;gap:10px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .cd-box{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:14px;padding:11px 18px;min-width:92px;text-align:center}
  .cd-num{font-family:var(--font-d);font-size:32px;font-weight:500;color:var(--rose-bright);line-height:1}
  .cd-lbl{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mauve);margin-top:4px}
  .cd-target{font-size:12px;color:var(--mauve);letter-spacing:.08em;margin-top:6px;text-align:center}

  nav{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:50;background:rgba(45,27,46,.88);backdrop-filter:blur(10px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);margin-top:18px}
  .nav-inner{display:flex;gap:4px;overflow-x:auto;padding:8px 0;scrollbar-width:none}
  .nav-inner::-webkit-scrollbar{display:none}
  .nav-btn{flex:0 0 auto;background:transparent;border:1px solid transparent;color:var(--mauve);
    font-family:var(--font-b);font-size:13px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.04em;padding:9px 15px;border-radius:999px;cursor:pointer;white-space:nowrap;transition:.18s}
  .nav-btn:hover{color:var(--ivory);border-color:var(--line)}
  .nav-btn.active{background:var(--rose);color:#fff;border-color:var(--rose)}

  section{display:none;padding:28px 0 10px;animation:fade .3s ease}
  section.show{display:block}
  @keyframes fade{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px)}to{opacity:1;transform:none}}
  h2.sec{font-family:var(--font-d);font-size:33px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:.04em;margin-bottom:4px}
  h2.sec .acc{color:var(--rose-bright)}
  .sec-sub{color:var(--mauve);font-size:14px;margin-bottom:22px;max-width:780px}
  h3.grp{font-family:var(--font-d);font-size:22px;font-weight:500;margin:26px 0 12px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}
  h3.grp::before{content:'';width:5px;height:22px;border-radius:3px;background:linear-gradient(var(--rose),var(--mauve))}

  .card{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:16px;padding:18px 20px;margin-bottom:14px}
  .grid{display:grid;gap:14px}
  @media(min-width:720px){.g3{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}.g2{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}}
  .stats{display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:14px}
  .stat{flex:1;min-width:120px;background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:14px;padding:14px 16px}
  .stat b{font-family:var(--font-d);font-size:30px;font-weight:500;color:var(--rose-bright);display:block;line-height:1}
  .stat span{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mauve)}
  .bar{height:8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);overflow:hidden;margin-top:8px}
  .bar>i{display:block;height:100%;border-radius:6px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--rose),var(--mauve));transition:width .4s}

  /* day / task */
  .day{border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:16px;margin-bottom:14px;overflow:hidden;background:var(--card)}
  .day-head{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;padding:13px 18px;background:rgba(183,110,121,.10);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);cursor:pointer}
  .day-head.weekend{background:rgba(201,160,176,.12)}
  .day.week-done .day-head, .day-head.done-all{background:rgba(95,185,143,.16)}
  .day-collapse{flex:0 0 18px;color:var(--mauve);font-size:13px;transition:.2s}
  .day.collapsed .day-collapse{transform:rotate(-90deg)}
  .day.collapsed .task,.day.collapsed .edit-row{display:none}
  .day-date{font-family:var(--font-d);font-size:19px;font-weight:500}
  .day-dow{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mauve)}
  .day-tally{margin-left:auto;font-size:12px;color:var(--mauve)}
  .day-tally.done-all{color:var(--ok);font-weight:700}
  .task{display:flex;gap:13px;align-items:flex-start;padding:11px 18px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(201,160,176,.08);cursor:pointer;transition:.15s}
  .task:last-child{border-bottom:none}
  .task:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.03)}
  .chk{flex:0 0 22px;width:22px;height:22px;border-radius:7px;border:2px solid var(--mauve);margin-top:1px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transition:.18s}
  .chk svg{width:13px;height:13px;opacity:0;transform:scale(.4);transition:.18s;color:#fff}
  .task.done .chk,.pend-item.done .chk{background:var(--ok);border-color:var(--ok)}
  .task.done .chk svg,.pend-item.done .chk svg{opacity:1;transform:scale(1)}
  .task.done .t-act,.pend-item.done .pi-text{text-decoration:line-through;color:var(--mauve)}
  .t-time{flex:0 0 96px;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;color:var(--rose-bright)}
  .t-body{flex:1;min-width:0}
  .t-act{font-size:14px;font-weight:500}
  .t-tema{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--mauve);margin-top:2px}
  .pill{display:inline-block;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:999px;margin-left:6px;vertical-align:middle}
  .p-q{background:rgba(183,110,121,.22);color:var(--rose-bright)}
  .p-rev{background:rgba(95,185,143,.18);color:var(--ok)}
  .p-teo{background:rgba(201,160,176,.18);color:var(--mauve)}
  .p-sim{background:rgba(216,166,87,.2);color:var(--warn)}
  .edited-tag{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--warn);margin-left:6px}
  .t-edit{flex:0 0 28px;width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid var(--line);background:transparent;color:var(--mauve);cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transition:.15s;margin-top:-2px}
  .t-edit:hover{border-color:var(--rose);color:var(--rose-bright)}
  .t-edit svg{width:14px;height:14px}
  .edit-row{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;align-items:center;padding:11px 18px;background:rgba(183,110,121,.08);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(201,160,176,.08)}
  .edit-row input{background:var(--plum-2);border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--ivory);border-radius:8px;padding:8px 10px;font-family:var(--font-b);font-size:13px}
  .edit-row .in-time{flex:0 0 110px}.edit-row .in-act{flex:1;min-width:150px}.edit-row .in-tema{flex:1;min-width:150px}
  .ebtn{border-radius:8px;padding:8px 14px;font-family:var(--font-b);font-size:12.5px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--line);background:transparent;color:var(--ivory)}
  .ebtn.save{background:var(--rose);border-color:var(--rose);color:#fff}
  .ebtn.del{color:#e79a9a;border-color:rgba(215,122,122,.4)}

  .week-ribbon{margin-left:auto;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ok);
    background:rgba(95,185,143,.16);border:1px solid rgba(95,185,143,.4);padding:4px 12px;border-radius:999px;display:none}
  h3.grp.week-complete{color:#7fd0a6}
  h3.grp.week-complete::before{background:var(--ok)}
  h3.grp.week-complete .week-ribbon{display:inline-block}

  .note{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--mauve);background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);border-left:3px solid var(--rose);border-radius:0 10px 10px 0;padding:11px 14px;margin:6px 0 16px}
  .legend{display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:18px}
  .legend span{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ivory);background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--line);padding:8px 14px;border-radius:999px}
  .dot{width:16px;height:16px;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;flex:0 0 16px;box-shadow:0 0 0 2px rgba(0,0,0,.18)}
  .dot.sq{border-radius:5px}
  .empty{text-align:center;color:var(--mauve);padding:36px 10px}

  /* calendar */
  .cal-month{margin-bottom:24px}
  .cal-title{font-family:var(--font-d);font-size:24px;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:10px;text-transform:capitalize}
  .cal-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(7,1fr);gap:6px}
  .cal-dow{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mauve);text-align:center;padding:4px 0}
  .cal-cell{aspect-ratio:1;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:10px;padding:6px;font-size:12px;cursor:pointer;transition:.15s;min-height:58px;display:flex;flex-direction:column}
  .cal-cell.empty-cell{border:none;cursor:default}
  .cal-cell:hover{border-color:var(--rose);transform:translateY(-2px)}
  .cal-cell .d{font-weight:700;font-size:13px}
  .cal-cell.today{outline:2px solid var(--rose-bright);outline-offset:1px}
  .cal-cell.done{background:var(--ok-bg)}
  .cal-dots{margin-top:auto;display:flex;gap:4px;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .cal-dots i{width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;box-shadow:0 0 0 1.5px rgba(0,0,0,.2)}

  /* ranking */
  .rk-list{display:grid;gap:9px}
  .rk-card{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--line);border-left-width:5px;border-radius:12px;padding:13px 16px}
  .rk-card.urgent{border-left-color:#e79a9a}.rk-card.imp{border-left-color:var(--warn)}
  .rk-card.good{border-left-color:#7fd0a6}.rk-card.low{border-left-color:#7fd0a6}
  .rk-top{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .rk-name{font-family:var(--font-d);font-size:19px;font-weight:500}
  .rk-meta{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;font-size:12px;color:var(--mauve);margin-top:4px}
  .rk-stars{color:var(--warn);letter-spacing:3px;font-size:15px}
  .studied-btn{border:1px solid var(--line);background:transparent;color:var(--mauve);border-radius:999px;padding:6px 13px;font-family:var(--font-b);font-size:12px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;white-space:nowrap;transition:.15s}
  .studied-btn.on{background:var(--ok);border-color:var(--ok);color:#fff}
  .area-head{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;cursor:pointer;margin:26px 0 12px}
  .area-head .arw{color:var(--mauve);transition:.2s;font-size:14px}
  .area-head.collapsed .arw{transform:rotate(-90deg)}
  .area-head h3{font-family:var(--font-d);font-size:22px;font-weight:500;margin:0}
  .area-head .cnt{font-size:12px;color:var(--mauve)}
  .area-body.collapsed{display:none}

  /* pendĂȘncias */
  .pend-item{display:flex;gap:13px;align-items:flex-start;background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:12px;padding:12px 16px;margin-bottom:9px;cursor:pointer}
  .pend-item:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.03)}
  .pi-text{flex:1;font-size:14px;font-weight:500}
  .pi-tag{font-size:11px;color:var(--mauve);margin-top:2px}
  .pend-add{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-top:10px}
  .pend-add input{flex:1;background:var(--plum-2);border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--ivory);border-radius:10px;padding:11px 14px;font-family:var(--font-b);font-size:14px}

  /* radar + modo enare */
  .radar-wrap{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:20px;align-items:center}
  .radar-svg{flex:0 0 340px;max-width:100%}
  .enare-list{display:grid;gap:10px;margin-top:6px}
  .enare-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px}
  .enare-name{flex:0 0 130px;font-size:13.5px;font-weight:600}
  .enare-bar{flex:1;height:14px;border-radius:8px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);overflow:hidden}
  .enare-bar>i{display:block;height:100%;border-radius:8px}
  .enare-pct{flex:0 0 46px;text-align:right;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;font-weight:700}
  .enare-overall{text-align:center;padding:18px}
  .enare-overall b{font-family:var(--font-d);font-size:60px;font-weight:500;color:var(--rose-bright);line-height:1;display:block}

  /* pomodoro */
  #pomo-stage{transition:.3s}
  .pomo-circle{width:280px;height:280px;border-radius:50%;margin:10px auto 18px;position:relative;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
    background:radial-gradient(circle at 50% 40%,rgba(183,110,121,.16),rgba(201,160,176,.04));border:1px solid var(--line)}
  .pomo-time{font-family:var(--font-d);font-size:78px;font-weight:300;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;color:var(--ivory);letter-spacing:.02em}
  .pomo-mode{text-align:center;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.25em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mauve);margin-bottom:4px}
  .pomo-ctrls{display:flex;gap:10px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:6px}
  .pbtn{border:1px solid var(--line);background:transparent;color:var(--ivory);border-radius:999px;padding:11px 22px;font-family:var(--font-b);font-size:14px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;transition:.15s}
  .pbtn:hover{border-color:var(--rose)}
  .pbtn.primary{background:var(--rose);border-color:var(--rose);color:#fff}
  .pomo-cfg{display:flex;gap:14px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:18px;color:var(--mauve);font-size:13px}
  .pomo-cfg label{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
  .pomo-cfg input{width:58px;background:var(--plum-2);border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--ivory);border-radius:8px;padding:6px 8px;text-align:center}
  .pomo-cycles{text-align:center;color:var(--mauve);font-size:13px;margin-top:10px}
  /* anti-distraĂ§ĂŁo */
  #pomo-stage.zen .pomo-mode,#pomo-stage.zen .pomo-cfg,#pomo-stage.zen .pomo-cycles,#pomo-stage.zen .zen-hide{display:none}
  #pomo-stage.zen .pomo-circle{width:340px;height:340px}
  #pomo-stage.zen .pomo-time{font-size:104px}
  #pomo-stage:fullscreen{background:var(--plum);display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;height:100%}
  #pomo-stage:fullscreen .pomo-circle{width:min(60vh,420px);height:min(60vh,420px)}
  #pomo-stage:fullscreen .pomo-time{font-size:min(18vh,128px)}
  .pomo-toggles{display:flex;gap:10px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:16px}

  .toast{position:fixed;bottom:24px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(20px);background:var(--plum-soft);border:1px solid var(--rose);color:var(--ivory);padding:11px 20px;border-radius:999px;font-size:13px;opacity:0;transition:.3s;z-index:200;pointer-events:none}
  .toast.show{opacity:1;transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(0)}
  .reset{background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--mauve);border-radius:999px;padding:7px 14px;font-family:var(--font-b);font-size:12px;cursor:pointer}
  .reset:hover{border-color:var(--urgent);color:#e79a9a}
  .footer{text-align:center;color:var(--mauve);font-size:12px;padding:40px 0 10px}
  .footer .ded{font-size:18px;margin-top:6px}
  /* gate + topbar */
  .gate{position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:300;background:var(--plum);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;text-align:center;padding:24px}
  .gate-card{max-width:430px}
  .spinner{width:42px;height:42px;border-radius:50%;border:3px solid rgba(201,160,176,.25);border-top-color:var(--rose);animation:spin 1s linear infinite;margin:0 auto 18px}
  @keyframes spin{to{transform:rotate(360deg)}}
  .gate .brand{font-family:var(--font-d);font-size:46px;font-weight:300;letter-spacing:.18em}
  .gate-btn{display:inline-block;margin-top:20px;background:var(--rose);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:999px;padding:13px 28px;font-family:var(--font-b);font-weight:600;font-size:14px;cursor:pointer;text-decoration:none}
  .gate-btn:hover{background:var(--rose-bright)}
  .topbar{display:none;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:12px;padding:10px 20px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);background:rgba(45,27,46,.55)}
  .tb-left,.tb-right{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}
  .tb-btn{border:1px solid var(--line);background:transparent;color:var(--mauve);border-radius:999px;padding:8px 14px;font-family:var(--font-b);font-size:12.5px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;transition:.15s}
  .tb-btn:hover{border-color:var(--rose);color:var(--ivory)}
  .tb-power{width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:16px;border:1px solid var(--line);background:transparent;color:var(--rose-bright);cursor:pointer;transition:.15s}
  .tb-power:hover{border-color:var(--rose);background:rgba(183,110,121,.12)}
  .tb-user{font-size:12px;color:var(--mauve);max-width:190px;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;white-space:nowrap}
  .tb-exit{border-color:rgba(215,122,122,.4);color:#e79a9a}
  .tb-exit:hover{border-color:var(--urgent);color:#e79a9a}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="gate" id="gate">
  <div class="gate-card">
    <div id="gate-loading">
      <div class="spinner"></div>
      <div style="color:var(--mauve);letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:12px">Carregando sua sessĂŁo ELIDâŠ</div>
    </div>
    <div id="gate-login" style="display:none">
      <svg width="40" height="56" viewBox="0 0 40 56" fill="none" stroke="var(--rose)" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:block;margin:0 auto 12px">
        <line x1="20" y1="3" x2="20" y2="53"/><path d="M20 9c-7 0-7 6 0 6s7 6 0 6-7 6 0 6 7 6 0 6"/><path d="M20 9c7 0 7 6 0 6s-7 6 0 6 7 6 0 6-7 6 0 6"/>
      </svg>
      <div class="brand"><span style="color:var(--rose-bright)">E</span>LI<span style="color:var(--rose-bright)">D</span></div>
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-d);font-size:25px;margin-top:12px">Acesso pelo ELID</div>
      <p style="color:var(--mauve);font-size:14px;margin-top:10px">Entre pela plataforma ELID para acessar seu cronograma. Suas tarefas, mĂ©tricas e progresso ficam salvos na sua conta e sincronizam entre dispositivos.</p>
      <a class="gate-btn" href="../../landing-page/">Ir para o ELID â</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="app" style="display:none">
<div class="topbar" id="topbar">
  <div class="tb-left">
    <button class="tb-power" id="tb-back" title="Voltar Ă  Biblioteca ELID">â»</button>
    <button class="tb-btn" id="tb-back2">â Biblioteca</button>
  </div>
  <div class="tb-right">
    <span class="tb-user" id="elid-user"></span>
    <button class="tb-btn tb-exit" id="tb-exit">Sair do ELID</button>
  </div>
</div>
<header>
  <div class="wrap">
    <svg class="rod" width="38" height="54" viewBox="0 0 40 56" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
      <line x1="20" y1="3" x2="20" y2="53"/>
      <path d="M20 9c-7 0-7 6 0 6s7 6 0 6-7 6 0 6 7 6 0 6"/>
